   570→   * is browser-specific, but in general it will return an appropriate representation of the
   571→   * Interval in the assigned locale. Defaults to the system's locale if no locale has been
   572→   * specified.
   573→   * @see https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DateTimeFormat
   574→   * @param {Object} [formatOpts=DateTime.DATE_SHORT] - Either a DateTime preset or
   575→   * Intl.DateTimeFormat constructor options.
